A simple app that intelligently turns off Auto Rotate of the phone's display when you're in bed.

Do you find yourself browsing the web or chatting with friends just before you lclose your eyes and be ready for a good dream, and find the display of the phone orienting the wrong way? That's where InBed comes in. It knows you're in bed and will turn it off for you, automagically. Try it tonight. Hope you'll like it.
